<h2 id="个人脚本-unrar-sh"><a href="#个人脚本-unrar-sh" class="headerlink" title="个人脚本 unrar.sh"></a>个人脚本 <a href="https://suqiguniang.github.io/others/others/unrar.sh">unrar.sh</a></h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">unrar.sh</span><br><span class="line">配合crontab自动解压文件并删除文件</span><br><span class="line">cosplaytele</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
